Oh, attends.

00:01:36.238 --> 00:01:37.420
Non!

00:01:37.445 --> 00:01:38.917
Attends, attends, attends.

00:01:40.234 --> 00:01:41.854
Oh, allez !

00:02:06.588 --> 00:02:08.010
Tu devrais me remercier.

00:02:08.034 --> 00:02:10.302
