00:03:48.389 --> 00:03:49.743
Je vais te donner un gros conseil.

00:03:50.816 --> 00:03:52.050
Merci beaucoup.

00:03:56.436 --> 00:03:57.445
Euh, hé toi.

00:03:57.478 --> 00:03:58.499
À propos d'hier soir

00:03:58.584 --> 00:04:00.882
